title: Paul Scheele - Natural Brilliance (Complete [audio + pdf's])
description:
Some blurb:

***

"Use the Natural Brilliance Personal Learning Course to overcome all challenges in your life, at will. You will receive 12 sessions on six CDs, a 48-page guide, and free coaching. Six of the audio sessions are special Paraliminal learning sessions designed specifically by Paul Scheele to help you automatically use your Natural Brilliance.

You will discover:

    Life becomes smoother and more fulfilling
    Proverbial mountains shrink to molehills
    Relationships become more meaningful and rewarding
    Change becomes effortless and easier
    Stress drains from your life
    Goals are achieved, again and again
    Euphoria becomes a way of life "

***

Enjoy.
